padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;有一天他在街上捡到一个孩子，他欣喜异常，认为是上天赐给他唯一的礼物。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;老人将孩子带回家，用辛苦收来的空酒瓶，换钱买廉价的奶粉，让那个小女孩活了下来，女孩在6岁的时候捡了一条小狗，取名旺才。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;小狗，聋哑老人，小女孩相依为命地生活在一起，小女孩的童年就在那一堆如山的空酒瓶中成长。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;天生的好嗓子让她成为聋哑人的传话机，在每个清晨女孩牵着老人，拄着拐杖。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;女孩大声的喊着：酒干倘卖无、酒干倘卖无。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;再后来，小女孩长大了，恋爱了，她爱上了一个作词家。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;年青的作词家一穷二白，但很爱她，带她走进了艺术天地，为她写了很多歌，对老人也非常好，每次来都会帮老人运酒瓶，和老人比划着说话，逗旺才......&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;word-wrap: break-word; border: 0px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jzw.tv/data/attachment/portal/201611/04/082618gt2mxvmp3c3rttr2.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(96, 113, 126);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.jzw.tv/data/attachment/portal/201611/04/082618gt2mxvmp3c3rttr2.jpg&quot; data-bd-imgshare-binded=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: none; max-width: 840px;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;然而有一天，女孩成名了，生活发生了质的变化，房子，汽车，周围追求的人......女孩还是很爱男孩，劝他和她一起住进大别墅，不要回酒瓶屋了，因为又聋又哑的父亲，让她觉得羞辱！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;男孩不愿意，仍和老人来往，后来女孩越来越忙，名气越来越大，生活完全由经济人安排。老人想念女儿，央求男孩带他去找女儿，但是还没进演唱会的大门就被轰出来了......&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;再后来女孩也烦了，丢给老头一笔钱让他不要再打扰，老人擦干了含泪的眼睛，没要女孩的一分钱，走时还留下女孩一直爱吃的一小袋松子！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;男孩看不过去了，找女孩理论，女孩心里听不进任何劝言，因为两人地位悬殊，最终只能分手。但老人终因思念女孩终于病倒了，男孩只好央求女孩，希望她能回家看看老人，女孩没听他的！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;就在这时，男孩打听到女孩唱歌的地方，他告诉了老人，老人挣扎着要去看女儿最后一面。不料走在路上，一辆卡车飞驰过来，眼看就要撞着老人了，老狗旺才猛地拱向了老人，旺才就这样死了。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;男孩知道后决定为女孩写最后一首歌，他连夜赶，顶着长期的贫困和思念，在他身体快不行的时候，写下了这首歌，让人送给了那个女孩。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;男孩写完歌词后也离开了人世间，演唱会上女孩不情愿地打开纸条，这首歌的歌词大意是：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;多么熟悉的声音，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;陪我多少年风和雨，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;从来不需要想起，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;永远也不会忘记。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;没有天哪有地，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-s