39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;酒干倘卖无，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;酒干倘卖无...........&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;多年前的往事一一在现，堆积如山的空酒瓶，聋哑的父亲，为了给她买一包松子累晕在酷暑的街头，还有小狗旺才拖着尾巴和她玩耍！......女孩哭了，她终于良心发现，愧疚，伤心，不安！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;她反复学着这首歌，最后登台的时候，她通知乐队加最后一首歌《酒干倘卖无》。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;女孩忘情地唱着，台下所有的人震惊了，所有的人都流下了眼泪，女孩在台上讲述了自己的身世，然后不顾一切地跑向了医院，她要见自己的父亲。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;当老人看到女儿时，一行老泪缓缓从腮边流下，老人什么也说不出口，只是微笑的看着女儿，慢慢的闭上了眼睛，女孩撕心裂肺的哭喊着，泣不成声......&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;这就是《酒干倘卖无》，一个真实的故事......&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(251, 5, 2); font-size: 20px; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;百善孝为先！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 41, 65); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;献给所有人！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;也许，我们的父母，不曾带给我们优越的环境和更多的财务，但是他们却尽最大的能力，把我们养大，把他们最好的时光和经历都给了我们。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;从呱呱坠地到咿呀学语，从慢慢会爬到渐渐行走，再到长大成人，他们付出了毕生经历和心血。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(217, 33, 66); word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;&gt;好好爱我们的父母吧，父母的养育恩，我们一辈子也报答不完。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;lt;p style=&amp;quot;border: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 2', '10', '1478418521');
INSERT INTO `blog_article` VALUES ('18', '要嫁就嫁程序猿——钱多话少死的早（此篇日志送给那些已经在坑里的或准备入坑的人）', '程序猿问科比：“你为什么这么成功？ ”科比：“你知道洛杉矶凌晨四点是什么样子吗？ ”程序猿：“知道，一般那个时候我还在写代码，怎么了？”科比：“额…….”', './Public/Uploads/2016-11-06/581ee2026fdf2.jpg', '&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;一、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;程序猿问科比：“你为什么这么成功？ ”&lt;br/&gt;科比：“你知道洛杉矶凌晨四点是什么样子吗？ ”&lt;br/&gt;程序猿：“知道，一般那个时候我还在写代码，怎么了？”&lt;br/&gt;科比：“额…….”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;二、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;女神：你能让这个论坛的人都吵起来，我今晚就跟你走。&lt;br/&gt;程序猿：PHP语言是最好的语言！&lt;br/&gt;论坛炸锅了，各种吵架。&lt;br/&gt;女神：服了你了，我们走吧，你想干啥都行。&lt;br/&gt;程序猿：今天不行，我一定要说服他们，PHP语言是最好的语言。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-original=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640.jpg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; src=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640.jpg&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;328&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;三、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;我是一个苦b的程序员，今晚加班到快通宵了，困得快睁不开眼了，女上司很关心，问我要不要吃宵夜。我没好气地说，宵夜就算了，能让我睡一觉就行了。女上司红着脸说了句讨厌啊，然后坐在我身边不动，好像距离我很近，搞得我很紧张，难道她发现我的程序出了bug？&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;四、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;老公一定要找程序员！！！！！！&lt;br/&gt;钱多话少死的早&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-original=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640_003.jpg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; src=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640_003.jpg&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;334&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;五、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;老婆给当程序员的老公打电话：“下班顺路买一斤包子带回来，如果看到卖西瓜的，就买一个。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;当晚，程序员老公手捧一个包子进了家门……&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;老婆怒道：“你怎么就买了一个包子？！”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;老公答曰：“因为看到了卖西瓜的。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;六、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-original=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640_004.jpg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; src=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640_004.jpg&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;&quot; width=&quot;460&quot; height=&quot;463&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;七、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;某人发帖子：“各位JR，我想做一个程序猿，请问有什么要注意的……”&lt;br/&gt;某猿：“等我下班跟你细说……”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;然后……就没有然后了&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;八、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-original=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640_002.jpg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; src=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640_002.jpg&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; height=&quot;1077&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;我问程序员朋友借了1000，他说再多借你24吧，凑个整&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;九、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;程序员A: “我吃鱼香肉丝盖饭, 你吃什么?”&lt;br/&gt;程序员B: “宫保鸡丁盖饭.”&lt;br/&gt;程序员A 在点菜单写上：&lt;br/&gt;鱼香肉丝盖饭 1&lt;br/&gt;宫保鸡丁盖饭 1&lt;br/&gt;程序员B: “我还是要牛肉面吧!”&lt;br/&gt;程序员A 更正点菜单:&lt;br/&gt;鱼香肉丝盖饭 1&lt;br/&gt;// 宫保鸡丁盖饭 1&lt;br/&gt;牛肉面 1&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;十、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;我是一个程序猿，一天我坐在路边一边喝水一边苦苦检查bug，这时一个乞丐在我边上坐下了，开始要饭，我觉得他可怜，就给了他一块钱，然后接着调试程序。他可能生意不好，就无聊的看看我在干什么，然后过了一会，他幽幽说，这里少了一个分号。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;我惊奇的问：“你也懂这行啊” 乞丐说：“我以前就是做这个的。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-original=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640.png&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; src=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640.png&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; height=&quot;494&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;十一、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;某程序员退休后决定练习书法，于是重金购买文房四宝。一日，饭后突生雅兴，一番研墨拟纸，并点上上好檀香。定神片刻，泼墨挥毫，郑重地写下一行字：hello world！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;十二、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;搞IT太辛苦了，想换一行怎么办？”“敲一下Enter键。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;十三、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;程序员不喜欢乾隆的第八个儿子，因为八阿哥 bug&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;十四、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;一女同学在食堂吃饭时，一程序猿凑到旁边，“同学，我能和你说话不，我已经一个月没和女生说话了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;十五、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;两个程序员在聊天：“我昨天碰到个辣妹。我把她带回家，马上就开始如饥似渴地亲吻，她就坐在我的键盘上，然后……”“你在家里也有台电脑？CPU是什么型号的？”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: normal; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img data-original=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640_002.png&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; src=&quot;http://static.webhek.com/techug-res/uploads/2014/10/640_002.png&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;&quot; width=&quot;356&quot; height=&quot;263&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; outline: 0px; padding: 12px 9px 12px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: right; position: relative; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;十六、&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: &amp;#39;Microsoft YaHei&amp;#39;, 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;#39;, STHeiti, &amp;#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;#39;, SimSun, sans-serif, Lucida, Verdana, serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;&quot;&gt;程序员的读书历程：x 语言入门 —&amp;gt; x 语言应用实践 —&amp;gt; x 语言高阶编程 —&amp;gt; x 语言的科学与艺术 —&amp;gt; 编程之美 —&amp;gt; 编程之道 —&amp;gt; 编程之禅—&amp;gt; 颈椎病康复指南。&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br/&gt;（来源于网络）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '10', '1478418765');
